overview.en: DHO is the only governance TOKEN of DAO Hyperledger Omniverse ecosystem. It takes DAO organization as the first strategic drive and uses blockchain technology to build a complete Web3.0 ecosystem application system. Deep layout in hyperledger, Quantum computing, NFT, Metasverse, gameFi, etc.
overview.zh: DHO为 DAO Hyperledger Omniverse 生态的唯一治理TOKEN,以DAO组织作为第一战略驱动，运用区块链技术搭建一个完整的web3.0生态应用系统。将在超级账本，量子计算，NFT,元宇宙，gameFi等版块深度布局。
